{"tid":1003161,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[逆向思維]想用Smart Octopus,不如叫Samsung Pay 支援其他 smartphone","createTime":"2019-01-31T12:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T03:29:22.000Z","uid":205469,"like":8,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4e06004e7f494a020bd9ca45f812b03f38dfc884","tid":1003161,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:23:57.000Z","msg":"連登仔成日屌八達通，要求smart octopus 加入 Google Apple pay，點解唔要求Samsung Pay開放俾其他smart phone？<br />\n<br />\n八仔搵 三叔 合作係因為 三叔 肯俾錢幫八仔搞個system，唔想俾錢其他pay，三叔 同 八仔 合作係因為 想用八仔嘅普及性推廣Samsung pay同吸引多d人買Samsung機（因為Samsung pay 係Samsung機獨家）<br />\n<br />\n不過smart octopus 自17年12月推出以來，都唔見多咗人用Samsung Pay , 之前Samsung smart octopus 出增值優惠就證明唔係好掂，另外，samsung 機嘅市佔率不升反跌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UG3nAet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUG3nAet.png&h=65f6e010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他機嘅用家冇得用smart octopus,繼續屌八達通<br />\n<br />\n咁就證明香港人唔會為咗用smart octopus而轉用Samsung，既然係咁，不如叫Samsung pay 支援其他機，咁Samsung pay 又可以增加市佔率，香港人又唔洗繼續屌八達通"},{"pid":"576cb90be1c0590b35e5c6c98aa98b1927d2f317","tid":1003161,"uid":23792,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"真係幾逆向 逆到唔見埋"},{"pid":"72efc6f2f4e88408eabbd60c0aa4b46918ef2faa","tid":1003161,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"其實香港都未做到唔洗帶銀包出街 既然要帶銀包出街 袋埋8達通有咩所謂<br />\n唔太重要既功能"},{"pid":"de0ae51ecdd32f8c84587e489a86fdca48d08c82","tid":1003161,"uid":65888,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"72efc6f2f4e88408eabbd60c0aa4b46918ef2faa","tid":1003161,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"其實香港都未做到唔洗帶銀包出街 既然要帶銀包出街 袋埋8達通有咩所謂<br />\n唔太重要既功能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"你唔行佢唔行我都唔行，大家一齊唔好行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔怪得hk no it<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"